			<h4><a rel="nofollow" id="comment_link_65285487" name="comment_link_65285487" href="//science.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23658007&amp;cid=65285487" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(65285487)" >We could reach Mars at the speed of light-</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_65285487" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 65285487); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>5</a>, Funny)</span></h4>
