	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_65285487">-with quantum teleportation. See quantum teleportation exists wherein you can use entangled partices and a classical communication channel and you can teleport a quantum state from one place to another at the speed of light! We've already teleported entangled photons, but in principle there's no size limits on entangled states. Now all we need do is scale up entanglement to humans in spacesuit, send half the entangled states to mars with laser receiving apparatus, ensure 100% teleportation fidelity, and boom speed of light teleportation to Mars! If only these lazy "engineers" would get on fulfilling my brilliant vision now that I've done the hard part we'd solve this whole "landing on Mars" thing!</div>
